*** ACTION REQUIRED BEFORE PUBLISHING ***

This file is a placeholder. It does NOT contain the actual GNU GPL v3.0
license text yet, and must be replaced before you publish this repository.

To fix this (takes under a minute):

OPTION A - Let GitHub generate it for you (easiest):
  1. Push this repo to GitHub.
  2. On GitHub, click "Add file" -> "Create new file".
  3. Name the file exactly: LICENSE
  4. Click "Choose a license template" and select "GNU General Public
     License v3.0". GitHub will auto-fill the complete official text.
  5. Commit it - this replaces this placeholder file entirely.

OPTION B - Download it yourself:
  1. Go to https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt
  2. Save that page's content as LICENSE (no file extension) in this
     project's root folder, replacing this file.

Either way, do this before making the repository public - a placeholder
license file is worse than no license file at all, since it could be
mistaken for the real thing.
